    <h2>What Is a Full XL Mattress?</h2>

    <p><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 54" wide × 80" long</p>

    <p>A Full XL mattress is 5 inches longer than a standard Full/Double mattress while maintaining the same width. The 80-inch length matches a Queen, King, or Twin XL mattress — making it a universal fit for adults of all heights.</p>

    <p><strong>Important note:</strong> A Full XL is NOT the same as a Queen. Many people confuse these sizes. A Queen is 6 inches wider (60" vs 54"). If you're shopping for a Queen, this isn't it.</p>

